title: Handle for dolly cart

claims.preamble: The ornamental design of a handle for a dolly cart, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is an isometric view of a handle for a dolly cart in accordance with the present invention;
FIG. 2 is a front elevational view of the handle of FIG. 1;
FIG. 3 is a top plan view of the handle of FIG. 1;
FIG. 4 is a side elevational view of the handle of FIG. 1;
FIG. 5 is a rear elevational view of the handle of FIG. 1; and,
FIG. 6 is a bottom plan view of the handle of FIG. 1.
